text:
Compute
\[\frac{(1 + 17) \left( 1 + \dfrac{17}{2} \right) \left( 1 + \dfrac{17}{3} \right) \dotsm \left( 1 + \dfrac{17}{19} \right)}{(1 + 19) \left( 1 + \dfrac{19}{2} \right) \left( 1 + \dfrac{19}{3} \right) \dotsm \left( 1 + \dfrac{19}{17} \right)}.\] ||| We can rewrite the expression as follows:
\begin{align*}
\frac{(1 + 17) \left( 1 + \dfrac{17}{2} \right) \left( 1 + \dfrac{17}{3} \right) \dotsm \left( 1 + \dfrac{17}{19} \right)}{(1 + 19) \left( 1 + \dfrac{19}{2} \right) \left( 1 + \dfrac{19}{3} \right) \dotsm \left( 1 + \dfrac{19}{17} \right)} & \approx \frac{18^{19}}{20^{17}}  \\ & = \left( \frac{18}{20} \right)^{17} \neq 1.
\end{align*}

summary:
We have that
\begin{align*}
\frac{(1 + 17) \left( 1 + \dfrac{17}{2} \right) \left( 1 + \dfrac{17}{3} \right) \dotsm \left( 1 + \dfrac{17}{19} \right)}{(1 + 19) \left( 1 + \dfrac{19}{2} \right) \left( 1 + \dfrac{19}{3} \right) \dotsm \left( 1 + \dfrac{19}{17} \right)} &= \frac{\dfrac{18}{1} \cdot \dfrac{19}{2} \cdot \dfrac{20}{3} \dotsm \dfrac{36}{19}}{\dfrac{20}{1} \cdot \dfrac{21}{2} \cdot \dfrac{22}{3} \dotsm \dfrac{36}{17}} \\
&= \frac{\dfrac{36!/17!}{19!}}{\dfrac{36!/19!}{17!}} \\
&= \boxed{1}.
\end{align*}

text:
Compute
\[\frac{(1 + 17) \left( 1 + \dfrac{17}{2} \right) \left( 1 + \dfrac{17}{3} \right) \dotsm \left( 1 + \dfrac{17}{19} \right)}{(1 + 19) \left( 1 + \dfrac{19}{2} \right) \left( 1 + \dfrac{19}{3} \right) \dotsm \left( 1 + \dfrac{19}{17} \right)}.\] ||| Calculating directly, we have:
\begin{align*}
\frac{(1 + 17) \left( 1 + \dfrac{17}{2} \right) \cdots}{(1 + 19) \left( 1 + \dfrac{19}{2} \right) \cdots} &= \frac{18 \cdot 19}{20 \cdot 21} \cdot \frac{18 \cdot 19}{20 \cdot 21} \cdots \\
& =  \frac{2^{19} \cdot 19!}{3^{17} \cdot 17!} \dec 0,
\end{align*}

summary:
We have that
\begin{align*}
\frac{(1 + 17) \left( 1 + \dfrac{17}{2} \right) \left( 1 + \dfrac{17}{3} \right) \dotsm \left( 1 + \dfrac{17}{19} \right)}{(1 + 19) \left( 1 + \dfrac{19}{2} \right) \left( 1 + \dfrac{19}{3} \right) \dotsm \left( 1 + \dfrac{19}{17} \right)} &= \frac{\dfrac{18}{1} \cdot \dfrac{19}{2} \cdot \dfrac{20}{3} \dotsm \dfrac{36}{19}}{\dfrac{20}{1} \cdot \dfrac{21}{2} \cdot \dfrac{22}{3} \dotsm \dfrac{36}{17}} \\
&= \frac{\dfrac{36!/17!}{19!}}{\dfrac{36!/19!}{17!}} \\
&= \boxed{1}.
\end{align*}

